name: Defiance
absentee_method: Merged into voters' home precincts and released with cumulative results
poll_display_race: Polls close at 7:30 p.m. Eastern time.
expectations_text_race: Postmarked ballots have until Nov. 13 to arrive, but no additional results will be reported reported for at least a week and a half after the election.
